Author: Varyg
Title: [ANN][IMVR] ImmVRse - Decentralised Marketplace for VR Pros 🚀 - Listed on DDEX
Body: Security token is ideal for asset-backed companies and applications that deal with trading assets, stocks or CFDs. As a result, token holders can earn dividends or profit shares. With ImmVRse, we ideally want the token to be a utility within the ecosystem platforms we will build in the future as it's used as proof of access gayeway. Additionally, a security token will restrict a startup from raising funds through ICO from a lot of countries including Singapore and Switzerland due to recent regulations.

Body: A 2018 Guide To Investing in Initial Coin Offerings  There is a difference between and IPO, and ICO. That being if an investor participates in an IPO you own part of the company as a stock. On the other side of the spectrum, if an investor takes part in an ICO, you own a digital asset coin, that is issued by the company. Usually, the currency is some sort of utility token with its own specific role in the company's ecosystem trading between i.e a consumer, a content-maker and an advertiser.  The increasing demand rises the intrinsic value of the currency sometimes by tousands of percentage. To put this into perspective, the highest performing stock in the S&P 500 rose only 132% in 2017. Whist the top 20 best performing ICO’s rose by an incredible 20,000%. These kind of gains are never guaranteed and can come with a lot of price volatility.  Read the details in the article of Coinidol dot com, the world blockchain news outlet: https://coinidol.com/guide-to-investing-in-initial-coin-offerings/

Author: fabh_
Title: [ANN][IMVR] ImmVRse - Decentralised Marketplace for VR Pros 🚀 - Listed on DDEX
Body: In order to differentiate ourselves, I should say: 1. We are not only a VR content sharing platform, but also a marketplace for content creators. Companies use our decentralised search engine to find content creators and hire them using the ecosystem token called ImmVRse token.  2. We are using blockchain-based automated incentivised contracts - that is the users e.g. content creators/viewers will get paid for interacting with our application. The entire algorithm will be built around our ImmVRse Token. Similar to Clubcard points, our members will earn ImmVRse tokens to play.  3. Through us, the amateur VR content creators will be able to learn new skills from the experienced users via the ImmVRse academy  4. Possibly partnering with companies in the future who will accept IMV as a form of payment outside the ecosystem  Also, we might consider voting rights in the future.

Author: Vladdirescu87
Title: [ANN][IMVR] ImmVRse - Decentralised Marketplace for VR Pros 🚀 - Listed on DDEX
Body: Decentralised Marketplace And Content Sharing Platform ImmVRse are Poised To Disrupt The VR Industry  ImmVRse is a decentralised VR content sharing platform that will aim to offer creators of the content, VR brands and advertisers a chance to get their product or service out into the public space. The ImmVRse app will work as a marketplace and also a conventional distribution platform. The platform will have its very own native currency, the ImmVRse token (IMV), which will be used as the form of payment between all parties within the ecosystem.  Read the details in the article of Coinidol dot com, the world blockchain news outlet: https://coinidol.com/decentralised-marketplace-and-content-sharing-platform-immvrse-poised-to-disrupt-vr-industry/
